author: Bruce Jenkins
title: Rockies defeat Giants 9-3
text:
Photo: Thearon W. Henderson, Getty Images Chris Heston #53 of the San Francisco Giants reacts after giving up a two-run RBI double to Jose Reyes #7 of the Colorado Rockies in the top of the fourth inning at AT&T Park on October 2, 2015 in San Francisco, California. Chris Heston #53 of the San Francisco Giants reacts after giving up...
What’s left of the Giants’ season is a kind of checklist, monitoring not so much the scoreboard but certain players’ performances. Friday night was a mixed bag in that regard as the Colorado Rockies and the phenomenal Nolan Arenado pounded out a 9-3 victory at AT&T Park.
